    "_srcBlendFactor": 770,
    "_dstBlendFactor": 771,
    "_string": "🎓 You’ve finally reached the end...\n\nYou’ve laughed, cried, rushed deadlines, and survived finals.\n\nBut university wasn’t just about classes.\nIt was about friendship. Growth. Finding who you are.\n\nNow you’re ready to walk forward —\nnot because the world is easy,\nbut because you’ve learned how to face it.\n\nThank you for playing.\nCongratulations, Graduate.",
